https://leetcode.com/problems/convert-binary-number-in-a-linked-list-to-integer/description/?envType=problem-list-v2&envId=linked-list

class Solution {
    public int getDecimalValue(ListNode head) {
        int result = 0;
        ListNode curr = head;
        while (curr != null) {
            result = (result << 1) | curr.val; // shift left and add bit
            curr = curr.next;
        }
        return result;
    }
}

Example Dry Run
Input list: 1 → 0 → 1

Start: result = 0

Node 1: (0 << 1) | 1 = 1

Node 0: (1 << 1) | 0 = 2

Node 1: (2 << 1) | 1 = 5

Output: 5
